937
00:56:43,570 --> 00:56:45,070
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah, tunggu sebentar.</font>

938
00:56:45,070 --> 00:56:46,169
<font color=#FFFF00>Bangunlah!</font>

939
00:56:46,169 --> 00:56:47,899
<font color=#FFFF00>- Ayah.../- Kamu!</font>

940
00:56:49,200 --> 00:56:50,939
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga. Se Kyung!</font>

941
00:56:50,939 --> 00:56:53,070
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang kamu lakukan?</font>

942
00:56:53,070 --> 00:56:55,879
<font color=#FFFF00>Bangunlah dan kuatkan dirimu.</font>

943
00:56:55,879 --> 00:56:58,179
<font color=#FFFF00>Perusahaan akan segera hancur.</font>

944
00:56:58,179 --> 00:57:00,280
<font color=#FFFF00>- Ayo./- Tidak!</font>

945
00:57:00,320 --> 00:57:02,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Terlalu berbahaya jika dia pergi sekarang.</font>

946
00:57:02,020 --> 00:57:03,089
<font color=#FFFF00>Minggir!</font>

947
00:57:03,689 --> 00:57:05,720
<font color=#FFFF00>- Jangan, Pil Mo./- Lepaskan!</font>

948
00:57:06,720 --> 00:57:09,520
<font color=#FFFF00>- Bangunlah!/- Jangan, Pil Mo.</font>

949
00:57:10,359 --> 00:57:11,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Minggir, Deul Lae.</font>

950
00:57:12,060 --> 00:57:15,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia harus dihukum agar perusahaan selamat.</font>

951
00:57:15,060 --> 00:57:16,770
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi bukan begini caranya.</font>

952
00:57:16,770 --> 00:57:20,369
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak dengan tanganmu sendiri. Kelak kamu akan menyesal.</font>

953
00:57:20,369 --> 00:57:21,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Lalu siapa yang akan menghukumnya?</font>

954
00:57:21,740 --> 00:57:24,040
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku memang ayahnya, tapi aku juga pimpinan Gongryong.</font>

955
00:57:24,040 --> 00:57:27,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak bisa melihat pegawaiku mati kelaparan. Minggir!</font>

956
00:57:28,780 --> 00:57:30,909
<font color=#FFFF00>Kumohon sadarlah!</font>

957
00:57:35,720 --> 00:57:37,189
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia sakit.</font>

958
00:57:38,490 --> 00:57:40,689
<font color=#FFFF00>Putrimu sekarat.</font>

959
00:57:44,889 --> 00:57:46,189
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

960
00:57:46,659 --> 00:57:48,399
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan beri tahu dia, Deul Lae!</font>

961
00:57:48,399 --> 00:57:50,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak, aku harus memberitahunya.</font>

962
00:57:50,929 --> 00:57:54,599
<font color=#FFFF00>Orang tuamu akan berdosa jika dibiarkan seperti ini.</font>

963
00:57:55,099 --> 00:57:57,939
<font color=#FFFF00>Kamu akan membuatnya menderita selamanya</font>

964
00:57:59,109 --> 00:58:00,139
<font color=#FFFF00>Pil Mo.</font>

965
00:58:01,579 --> 00:58:02,839
<font color=#FFFF00>Se Kyung</font>

966
00:58:03,780 --> 00:58:05,609
<font color=#FFFF00>mengidap kanker payudara stadium akhir.</font>

967
00:58:06,750 --> 00:58:09,220
<font color=#FFFF00>Hidupnya tinggal sebentar lagi.</font>

